{"tid":545715,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無水奇招】河南屋苑停水1星期 居民搬雪返屋企","createTime":"2018-01-30T19:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T03:35:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16454661526ae59dbdbdcfd698e05fb14396c1ce","tid":545715,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517327600_f4d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517327600_f4d6.jpg&h=381186b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南省平頂山市一個屋苑，從上周二（23日）起開始停水，當地居民生活大受影響，有居民想到將屋外的積雪搬回家融化，作為臨時用水。<br />\n<br />\n這個小區貼出的通告指出，他們的供水水管在嚴寒天氣之下被凍斷，雖然已通知供水部門前來搶修，可是甚麼時候可以恢復，卻是難以確定，有居民埋怨：「我這多少天我都沒洗臉！」<br />\n「沒水的日子化（融）點雪水！」一名居民稱，他們從室外拿積雪回家，放在火爐上把雪融掉，便有一點水可用，「沖廁所可以利用」，「洗漱啥的都是弄點雪嘛」。可是，融掉的雪水有看上去灰灰的，居民都不敢用來煮食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180131/57774170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774170&d=j76Mz%2BdMnwm4dtScG9oTMrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=256e37f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180131%2F57774170&h=43916de5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180131/57774170</a>"},{"pid":"a59664b40b16e38b033e7a03a1e2de50b93a594a","tid":545715,"uid":87540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3eaua8e/7200005692376421158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3eaua8e%2F7200005692376421158.jpg&h=c4ff3304&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87fc44b3dd0c9c96cd037538f783aeebfe60bd81","tid":545715,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"污染到雪水都唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebe08f0fc5946d85b3a4d100dca5ab4c29c1904","tid":545715,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5562eee49f042fb85f5c71ef699b7d9dbb31b6","tid":545715,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"「灰灰的」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁落完雪空氣應該前所未有咁清新"}]}